<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>FT001 — Certificado de Cumplimiento EyCCL</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');
    @page { size: A4; margin: 15mm 18mm; }
    @media print { body { margin: 0; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; } .no-print { display: none !important; } }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #2D3436; line-height: 1.5; background: #f5f0eb; }
    .no-print { position: fixed; top: 20px; right: 20px; z-index: 100; display: flex; gap: 8px; }
    .no-print button, .no-print a { padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; border: none; }
    .no-print button { background: #E85D3A; color: #fff; }
    .no-print a { background: #fff; color: #333; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
    .page { max-width: 210mm; margin: 20px auto; background: #fff; padding: 20mm 22mm; box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .doc-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; border-bottom: 3px solid #E85D3A; padding-bottom: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .doc-header-left h1 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: #2D3436; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .doc-header-left h2 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #E85D3A; margin-top: 2px; }
    .doc-header-left .subtitle { font-size: 11px; color: #636E72; margin-top: 2px; }
    .doc-header-right { text-align: right; font-size: 10px; color: #636E72; }
    .doc-header-right .folio { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #E85D3A; }
    .section { margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: #E85D3A; border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgba(232,93,58,0.2); padding-bottom: 4px; margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
    .info-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0; }
    .info-grid .cell { padding: 5px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }
    .info-grid .cell-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: #636E72; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
    .info-grid .cell-value { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 1px; }
    .data-table th { background: #f8f6f3; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: #636E72; padding: 7px 8px; border: 1px solid #eee; text-align: left; }
    .data-table td { padding: 6px 8px; border: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 11px; }
    .data-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) { background: #fafaf8; }
    .cost-summary { background: rgba(232,93,58,0.04); border: 1.5px solid rgba(232,93,58,0.15); border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 18px; margin: 10px 0; }
    .cost-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 4px 0; font-size: 12px; }
    .cost-row.total { border-top: 2px solid #E85D3A; margin-top: 6px; padding-top: 8px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px; color: #E85D3A; }
    .declaration { background: #f8f6f3; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; font-size: 11px; color: #636E72; line-height: 1.6; }
    .firmas { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 50px; }
    .firma { text-align: center; width: 40%; }
    .firma-line { border-top: 1.5px solid #2D3436; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .firma-name { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; }
    .firma-role { font-size: 10px; color: #999; }
    .doc-footer { margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 9px; color: #B2BEC3; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="no-print">
    <button onclick="window.print()">Imprimir / PDF</button>
    <a href="/franquicia/<%= accion.id %>">Volver</a>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <div class="doc-header">
      <div class="doc-header-left">
        <h1>Certificado de Cumplimiento de Condiciones</h1>
        <h2>Evaluacion y Certificacion de Competencias Laborales</h2>
        <div class="subtitle"><%= org.name %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="doc-header-right">
        <div class="folio">FT001</div>
        Ley 20.267<br>
        Franquicia Tributaria SENCE
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">1. Centro de Evaluacion y Certificacion</div>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">Nombre CEC</div><div class="cell-value"><%= org.name %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">RUT</div><div class="cell-value"><%= org.rut || '-' %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">Region</div><div class="cell-value"><%= org.region || '-' %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">Email</div><div class="cell-value"><%= org.email || '-' %></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">2. Datos de la Empresa</div>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">Razon Social</div><div class="cell-value"><%= accion.empresa_nombre %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">RUT</div><div class="cell-value"><%= accion.empresa_rut %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">Direccion</div><div class="cell-value"><%= accion.empresa_direccion || '-' %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">Region</div><div class="cell-value"><%= accion.empresa_region || '-' %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">Responsable</div><div class="cell-value"><%= accion.responsable_nombre || '-' %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">RUT Responsable</div><div class="cell-value"><%= accion.responsable_rut || '-' %></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">3. Datos de la Accion</div>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">Perfil</div><div class="cell-value"><%= accion.profile_code || '' %> — <%= accion.profile_name || '-' %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">Tipo Actividad</div><div class="cell-value"><%= accion.tipo %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">Fecha Inicio</div><div class="cell-value"><%= accion.fecha_inicio || '-' %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">Fecha Termino</div><div class="cell-value"><%= accion.fecha_termino || '-' %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">Valor UCL</div><div class="cell-value">$<%= (accion.valor_ucl || 0).toLocaleString('es-CL') %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">Comite Bipartito</div><div class="cell-value"><%= accion.tiene_comite_bipartito ? 'SI' : 'NO' %></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">4. Participantes (<%= participantes.length %>)</div>
      <table class="data-table">
        <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>RUT</th><th>Nombre</th><th>Tramo</th><th>% Franq.</th><th>Copago</th><th>Resultado</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <% participantes.forEach((p, i) => { %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= i + 1 %></td>
            <td><%= p.rut %></td>
            <td><%= p.nombre %></td>
            <td><%= p.tramo_franquicia %></td>
            <td><%= p.porcentaje_franquicia %>%</td>
            <td>$<%= (p.copago || 0).toLocaleString('es-CL') %></td>
            <td><strong><%= p.resultado %></strong></td>
          </tr>
          <% }) %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">5. Resumen de Costos</div>
      <div class="cost-summary">
        <div class="cost-row"><span>Total Bruto</span><span>$<%= costos.totalBruto.toLocaleString('es-CL') %></span></div>
        <div class="cost-row"><span>Franquicia Tributaria SENCE</span><span style="color:#27AE60; font-weight:600;">-$<%= costos.totalFranquicia.toLocaleString('es-CL') %></span></div>
        <div class="cost-row"><span>Copago Trabajadores</span><span>-$<%= costos.totalCopago.toLocaleString('es-CL') %></span></div>
        <div class="cost-row total"><span>Costo Neto Empresa</span><span>$<%= costos.costoEmpresa.toLocaleString('es-CL') %></span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">6. Declaracion</div>
      <div class="declaration">
        El Centro de Evaluacion y Certificacion de Competencias Laborales (CEC) declara que cumple con las condiciones establecidas en la Ley 20.267 y la normativa vigente de ChileValora y SENCE para la ejecucion de la accion de Evaluacion y Certificacion de Competencias Laborales descrita en el presente documento. Se certifica que el CEC cuenta con evaluadores habilitados por ChileValora, procedimientos operacionales aprobados, y la infraestructura necesaria para llevar a cabo el proceso de evaluacion.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="firmas">
      <div class="firma">
        <div class="firma-line"></div>
        <div class="firma-name">Representante Legal CEC</div>
        <div class="firma-role"><%= org.name %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="firma">
        <div class="firma-line"></div>
        <div class="firma-name">Representante Empresa</div>
        <div class="firma-role"><%= accion.empresa_nombre %></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-footer">
      <div>FT001 — <%= org.name %></div>
      <div>Ley 20.267 — Sistema Nacional de Certificacion de Competencias Laborales</div>
      <div>CertificaDesk — <%= new Date().toISOString().substring(0,10) %></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
